  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Treatment of keloids scars is difficult and controversial. These keloids have a functional
      and aesthetic impact. A lot of treatment are described with a lot of relapses and
      aggravation. Authors report outcomes of the treatment with shaving and cryosurgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
